    public class InteriorNode
extends TreeNode
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents an interior node in the CONIKS binary Merkle prefix tree.

      • clone

        public TreeNode clone(TreeNode parent)
        Clones (i.e. duplicates) this interior node with the given parent tree node. It then recursively calls this function on the original interior node's two subtrees.

        This function is called as part of the CONIKS Merkle tree rebuilding process at the beginning of every epoch.

        Overrides:
        clone in class TreeNode
        Returns:
        The cloned interior node.
